        code clones before they turn to the dark side and start a war.
        Let's get your code under control and Git organized!
      p.
        You're hopefully familiar with Git and how it can help you manage your codebase.
        But when it comes to working with remote repositories like GitHub and Azure DevOps,
        there are some important file management strategies you should keep in mind to ensure
        that your work is organized and efficient.
      dl
        dt Folder Structure
        dd.
